headline: Marriott International Announces Outstanding Global Growth and Milestone Achievements in 2025
summary: Marriott International, Inc. (Nasdaq: MAR, "Marriott") is proud to announce another year of outstanding global growth in 2025, marked by new brand offerings, strategic global scaling, and thoughtful collaboration with hotel owners.
